{"tid":1493054,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"心目中已黑名單的深井診所","createTime":"2019-08-21T05:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T16:49:50.000Z","uid":173547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"46b7b1956b4c16bcf22cb0b6d3ed46bea6f2bae6","tid":1493054,"uid":173547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:49:09.000Z","msg":"相信深井人都知Fusion隔離有間診所<br />\n叫新都醫務中心<br />\n<br />\n話說我呢排成身皮膚出左啲似濕疹<br />\n番工前走近去左附近間診所睇<br />\n不過睇完真心幾嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由頭到尾個醫生同我講唔超過2句<br />\n我講完病情佢咩都無講 就同我講出去等攞藥<br />\n我問佢：「醫生我咩病」 佢先答<br />\n又唔會話洗唔洗戒口 可能要注意啲咩<br />\n完全無！！！！ 重點係成間診所得我一個病人<br />\n但個醫生就好似好唔耐煩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾我都唔想問個醫生 出去走去問個護士<br />\n好彩個護士會去答 唔會唔耐煩<br />\n最尾埋單2百幾睇症加100蚊藥膏<br />\n買左支藥膏 同買左個難受 都唔知睇左啲咩<br />\n呢間診所唔會再去🤗 black list<br />\n<br />\n不可一不可再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a66078f9e768fc1055f88ae3dd99a36242974fc","tid":1493054,"uid":207430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵鐘家輝 幾好"},{"pid":"9b7dd44415fbfd171413fe9a48944d8ee914fbb4","tid":1493054,"uid":122458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a66078f9e768fc1055f88ae3dd99a36242974fc","tid":1493054,"uid":207430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵鐘家輝 幾好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"啲藥勁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807c3be762bde7755b1521864184a53222145332","tid":1493054,"uid":207430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b7dd44415fbfd171413fe9a48944d8ee914fbb4","tid":1493054,"uid":122458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a66078f9e768fc1055f88ae3dd99a36242974fc","tid":1493054,"uid":207430,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"點解唔搵鐘家輝 幾好"},"c